      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "As an artisan, in your early life, you worked on a specialized craft in one of the Valley\u2019s villages. You are adept in the use of tools, and you know how to work with your hands. Artisan cards key off of and support your equipped"
        },
        {
