    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The Valley\u2019s artisans are responsible for crafting tools and mastering their construction. They handcraft items for their communities and teach others how to do the same. An apprenticeship with a master artisan can sometimes last up to twenty years."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Artisans often go on to become artificers as they turn their attention toward experimenting with new technology, but many also go on to to pursue other interests, where they craft tools of their trade unequaled by their peers."
        }
      ]
    }
